  <brief_title>Dose-Escalating Multiple Dose Study of PD-0360324 in Combination With Methotrexate in Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Subject and Investigator-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study to Investigate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of Multiple Intravenously Administered Doses of PD-0360324 in Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis Receiving Methotrexate</official_title>
